Question: Can you show me the players who scored more than 2 goals in one game? I’d like to see their player_id, name, match number, and how many goals they scored.
Generated SQL Query:
SELECT g.player_id, p.player_name, g.match_no, COUNT(g.goal_id) AS goals_scored
FROM goal_details g
JOIN player_mast p ON g.player_id = p.player_id
GROUP BY g.player_id, p.player_name, g.match_no
HAVING COUNT(g.goal_id) > 2
ORDER BY goals_scored DESC;
Expected SQL Query:
SELECT gd.player_id, pm.player_name, gd.match_no, COUNT(*) AS total_goals
  FROM goal_details gd
  JOIN player_mast pm ON gd.player_id = pm.player_id
  GROUP BY gd.player_id, pm.player_name, gd.match_no
  HAVING COUNT(*) > 2;

Question: Tolong tampilkan pemain yang mencetak lebih dari 2 gol dalam satu pertandingan. Saya mau lihat player_id, nama pemain, match_no, dan total golnya.
Generated SQL Query:
SELECT 
    g.player_id, 
    p.player_name, 
    g.match_no, 
    COUNT(g.goal_id) AS total_goals
FROM 
    goal_details g
JOIN 
    player_mast p ON g.player_id = p.player_id
GROUP BY 
    g.player_id, p.player_name, g.match_no
HAVING 
    COUNT(g.goal_id) > 2
ORDER BY 
    total_goals DESC;
Expected SQL Query:
SELECT gd.player_id, pm.player_name, gd.match_no, COUNT(*) AS total_goals
  FROM goal_details gd
  JOIN player_mast pm ON gd.player_id = pm.player_id
  GROUP BY gd.player_id, pm.player_name, gd.match_no
  HAVING COUNT(*) > 2;

Question: Show all matches where the final score was a draw. Display the match number.
Expected SQL Query:
SELECT 
    md1.match_no
FROM 
    match_details md1
JOIN 
    match_details md2
    ON md1.match_no = md2.match_no
    AND md1.team_id <> md2.team_id
WHERE 
    md1.goal_score = md2.goal_score
GROUP BY 
    md1.match_no, md1.goal_score
ORDER BY 
    md1.match_no;

Question: Tampilkan semua pertandingan yang berakhir imbang. Sertakan nomor pertandingan.
Generated SQL Query: SELECT match_no FROM match_details WHERE win_lose = 'D';
Expected SQL Query:
SELECT 
    md1.match_no
FROM 
    match_details md1
JOIN 
    match_details md2
    ON md1.match_no = md2.match_no
    AND md1.team_id <> md2.team_id
WHERE 
    md1.goal_score = md2.goal_score
GROUP BY 
    md1.match_no, md1.goal_score
ORDER BY 
    md1.match_no;

Question: Can you list referees who led more than 3 matches? I want their referee_id, name, and total matches they officiated.
Generated SQL Query:
SELECT r.referee_id, r.referee_name, COUNT(mm.match_no) AS total_matches
FROM referee_mast r
JOIN match_mast mm ON r.referee_id = mm.referee_id
GROUP BY r.referee_id, r.referee_name
HAVING COUNT(mm.match_no) > 3
ORDER BY total_matches DESC;
Expected SQL Query:
SELECT rm.referee_id, rm.referee_name, COUNT(*) AS total_matches
  FROM match_mast mm
  JOIN referee_mast rm ON mm.referee_id = rm.referee_id
  GROUP BY rm.referee_id, rm.referee_name
  HAVING COUNT(*) > 3;

Question: Saya ingin tahu wasit yang memimpin lebih dari 3 pertandingan. Tampilkan referee_id, nama wasit, dan jumlah pertandingan.
Generated SQL Query:
SELECT r.referee_id, r.referee_name, COUNT(mm.match_no) AS jumlah_pertandingan
FROM referee_mast r
JOIN match_mast mm ON r.referee_id = mm.referee_id
GROUP BY r.referee_id, r.referee_name
HAVING COUNT(mm.match_no) > 3
ORDER BY jumlah_pertandingan DESC;
Expected SQL Query:
SELECT rm.referee_id, rm.referee_name, COUNT(*) AS total_matches
  FROM match_mast mm
  JOIN referee_mast rm ON mm.referee_id = rm.referee_id
  GROUP BY rm.referee_id, rm.referee_name
  HAVING COUNT(*) > 3;

Question: Show me which players were both substituted in and out in the same game. Include player_id, name, and match number.
Generated SQL Query:
SELECT DISTINCT p.player_id, p.player_name, i.match_no
FROM player_in_out i
JOIN player_mast p ON i.player_id = p.player_id
WHERE i.in_out = 'I' AND EXISTS (
    SELECT 1 
    FROM player_in_out o 
    WHERE o.match_no = i.match_no 
    AND o.player_id = i.player_id 
    AND o.in_out = 'O'
);
Expected SQL Query:
SELECT DISTINCT pio.player_id, pm.player_name, pio.match_no
  FROM player_in_out pio
  JOIN player_mast pm ON pio.player_id = pm.player_id
  WHERE EXISTS (
  SELECT 1 FROM player_in_out p2
  WHERE p2.player_id = pio.player_id AND p2.match_no = pio.match_no
  AND p2.in_out != pio.in_out
  );

FROM player_mast p
JOIN player_in_out pio1 ON p.player_id = pio1.player_id AND pio1.in_out = 'I'
JOIN player_in_out pio2 ON p.player_id = pio2.player_id AND pio2.in_out = 'O' AND pio1.match_no = pio2.match_no;
Expected SQL Query:
SELECT DISTINCT pio.player_id, pm.player_name, pio.match_no
  FROM player_in_out pio
  JOIN player_mast pm ON pio.player_id = pm.player_id
  WHERE EXISTS (
  SELECT 1 FROM player_in_out p2
  WHERE p2.player_id = pio.player_id AND p2.match_no = pio.match_no
  AND p2.in_out != pio.in_out
  );

Question: Can you list teams that scored more goals than they conceded in the tournament? I want team_id, goal_for, goal_agnst, and goal_diff.
Tampilkan tim-tim yang jumlah gol masuknya lebih banyak dari gol kebobolannya. Saya butuh team_id, goal_for, goal_agnst, dan goal_diff.
Show me the venues where audience attendance reached the highest. I want venue_name, the city, and the max audience number. Sort from highest.
Generated SQL Query:
SELECT sv.venue_name, sc.city, mm.audence AS max_audience
FROM soccer_venue sv
JOIN soccer_city sc ON sv.city_id = sc.city_id
JOIN match_mast mm ON sv.venue_id = mm.venue_id
WHERE mm.audence = (SELECT MAX(audence) FROM match_mast)
ORDER BY max_audience DESC;
Expected SQL Query:
SELECT sv.venue_name, sc.city, MAX(mm.audence) AS max_audience
  FROM match_mast mm
  JOIN soccer_venue sv ON mm.venue_id = sv.venue_id
  JOIN soccer_city sc ON sv.city_id = sc.city_id
  GROUP BY sv.venue_name, sc.city
  ORDER BY max_audience DESC;

Question: Which matches had 3 or more players from the same team getting booked? Show match number, team_id, and how many players were booked.

    match_no, 
    team_id, 
    COUNT(player_id) AS players_booked
FROM 
    player_booked
GROUP BY 
    match_no, 
    team_id
HAVING 
    COUNT(player_id) >= 3
ORDER BY 
    match_no, 
    team_id;
Expected SQL Query:
SELECT match_no, team_id, COUNT(player_id) AS booked_count
  FROM player_booked
  GROUP BY match_no, team_id
  HAVING COUNT(player_id) > 2;

Question: Which players were both involved in goals and received bookings? Show their player_id, name, and how many goals and bookings.
Generated SQL Query:
SELECT 
    p.player_id,
    p.player_name,
    COUNT(DISTINCT g.goal_id) AS goals,
    COUNT(DISTINCT b.match_no || b.team_id || b.player_id || b.booking_time) AS bookings
FROM 
    player_mast p
LEFT JOIN 
    goal_details g ON p.player_id = g.player_id
LEFT JOIN 
    player_booked b ON p.player_id = b.player_id
GROUP BY 
    p.player_id, p.player_name
HAVING 
    COUNT(DISTINCT g.goal_id) > 0 AND COUNT(DISTINCT b.match_no || b.team_id || b.player_id || b.booking_time) > 0
ORDER BY 
    p.player_name;
Expected SQL Query:
SELECT
  p.player_id,
  p.player_name,
  COUNT(g.goal_id) AS goal_count,
  COUNT(b.match_no) AS booking_count
FROM player_mast AS p
LEFT JOIN goal_details AS g ON p.player_id = g.player_id
LEFT JOIN player_booked AS b ON p.player_id = b.player_id
GROUP BY p.player_id, p.player_name
HAVING COUNT(g.goal_id) > 0 AND COUNT(b.match_no) > 0;

Question: Siapa saja pemain yang pernah cetak gol dan juga kena kartu? Tampilkan player_id, nama, total gol dan jumlah kartu.

SELECT

    COUNT(DISTINCT g.goal_id) AS total_gol,
    COUNT(DISTINCT b.match_no || b.team_id || b.player_id || b.booking_time) AS jumlah_kartu
FROM 
    player_mast p
JOIN 
    goal_details g ON p.player_id = g.player_id
JOIN 
    player_booked b ON p.player_id = b.player_id
GROUP BY 
    p.player_id, p.player_name
HAVING 
    COUNT(DISTINCT g.goal_id) > 0 AND COUNT(DISTINCT b.match_no || b.team_id || b.player_id || b.booking_time) > 0
ORDER BY 
    p.player_id;
Expected SQL Query:
SELECT
  p.player_id,
  p.player_name,
  COUNT(g.goal_id) AS goal_count,
  COUNT(b.match_no) AS booking_count
FROM player_mast AS p
LEFT JOIN goal_details AS g ON p.player_id = g.player_id
LEFT JOIN player_booked AS b ON p.player_id = b.player_id

Question: Which referees handled matches with average audience over 40,000? I want referee_id, name, and average audience.
Generated SQL Query:
SELECT r.referee_id, r.referee_name, AVG(m.audence) AS average_audience
FROM referee_mast r
JOIN match_mast m ON r.referee_id = m.referee_id
GROUP BY r.referee_id, r.referee_name
HAVING AVG(m.audence) > 40000
ORDER BY average_audience DESC;
Expected SQL Query:
SELECT rm.referee_id, rm.referee_name, AVG(mm.audence) AS avg_audience
  FROM match_mast mm
  JOIN referee_mast rm ON mm.referee_id = rm.referee_id
  GROUP BY rm.referee_id, rm.referee_name
  HAVING AVG(mm.audence) > 40000;

Question: Which captains also managed to score unique goals? I want to see their player_id, name, number of goals, and how many matches they were captain.
Generated SQL Query:
SELECT 
    pm.player_id,
    pm.player_name,
    COUNT(DISTINCT gd.goal_id) AS number_of_goals,
    COUNT(DISTINCT mc.match_no) AS matches_as_captain
FROM 
    player_mast pm
JOIN 
    match_captain mc ON pm.player_id = mc.player_captain
JOIN 
    goal_details gd ON pm.player_id = gd.player_id
GROUP BY 
    pm.player_id, pm.player_name
HAVING 
    COUNT(DISTINCT gd.goal_id) > 0
ORDER BY 
    number_of_goals DESC, matches_as_captain DESC;
Expected SQL Query:
SELECT mc.player_captain AS player_id, pm.player_name,
  COUNT(DISTINCT gd.goal_id) AS total_goals,
  COUNT(DISTINCT mc.match_no) AS total_captain_matches
  FROM match_captain mc
  JOIN goal_details gd ON mc.player_captain = gd.player_id
  JOIN player_mast pm ON mc.player_captain = pm.player_id
  GROUP BY mc.player_captain, pm.player_name;

Question: Siapa aja pemain yang jadi kapten sekaligus mencetak goal? Tampilkan player_id, nama, jumlah gol yang unik, dan berapa kali dia jadi kapten di pertandingan yang unik.
Generated SQL Query:
SELECT 
    pm.player_id,
    pm.player_name,
    COUNT(DISTINCT gd.match_no) AS unique_goals_scored,
    COUNT(DISTINCT mc.match_no) AS unique_captain_appearances
FROM 
    player_mast pm
JOIN 
    match_captain mc ON pm.player_id = mc.player_captain
JOIN 
    goal_details gd ON pm.player_id = gd.player_id
GROUP BY 
    pm.player_id, pm.player_name
HAVING 
    COUNT(DISTINCT gd.match_no) > 0
ORDER BY 
    unique_goals_scored DESC, unique_captain_appearances DESC;
Expected SQL Query:
SELECT mc.player_captain AS player_id, pm.player_name,
  COUNT(DISTINCT gd.goal_id) AS total_goals,
  COUNT(DISTINCT mc.match_no) AS total_captain_matches
  FROM match_captain mc
  JOIN goal_details gd ON mc.player_captain = gd.player_id
  JOIN player_mast pm ON mc.player_captain = pm.player_id
  GROUP BY mc.player_captain, pm.player_name;

Question: Which matches had all goals scored in the first half only? Show match number and number of goals.

Question: Kota mana yang punya pertandingan dengan lebih dari 4 gol? Saya mau lihat nama kota dan match_no-nya.
Generated SQL Query:
SELECT sv.venue_name, mm.match_no
FROM soccer_venue sv
JOIN match_mast mm ON sv.venue_id = mm.venue_id
JOIN (
    SELECT match_no, SUM(CAST(SUBSTRING(goal_score, 1, 1) AS INTEGER) + CAST(SUBSTRING(goal_score, 3, 1) AS INTEGER)) AS total_goals
    FROM match_mast
    GROUP BY match_no
    HAVING SUM(CAST(SUBSTRING(goal_score, 1, 1) AS INTEGER) + CAST(SUBSTRING(goal_score, 3, 1) AS INTEGER)) > 4
) AS high_scoring_matches ON mm.match_no = high_scoring_matches.match_no
ORDER BY total_goals DESC;
Expected SQL Query:
SELECT DISTINCT sc.city, gd.match_no
  FROM goal_details gd
  JOIN match_mast mm ON gd.match_no = mm.match_no
  JOIN soccer_venue sv ON mm.venue_id = sv.venue_id
  JOIN soccer_city sc ON sv.city_id = sc.city_id
  GROUP BY sc.city, gd.match_no
  HAVING COUNT(gd.goal_id) > 4;
